{"tid":1507840,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"冷氣機有曱甴","createTime":"2019-08-26T10:18:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T10:22:35.000Z","uid":200256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"86f289a29ff5d2da1a3bcd32441fd158dfb8151f","tid":1507840,"uid":200256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T10:18:50.000Z","msg":"之前已經試過幾次一開冷氣就有曱甴跌出嚟。跟住就洗冷氣，但過咗一排，琴日夜晚又跌咗一隻<br />\n     <br />\n     先發現我之前洗冷氣以為嗰啲係灰塵。原來係曱甴嘅排泄物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但我洗冷氣又搵唔到有巢或者蛋。間房基本上冇食過嘢，究竟點搞。"},{"pid":"c77f9d373587bef0a3523766f6592d39fda07b62","tid":1507840,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T10:19:20.000Z","msg":"唔好意思借個post宣傳一下<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4GJMrJb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4GJMrJb.jpg&h=cb7c9807&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n901 和你塞  13:00 見   <a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=TNp%2FFCzVUvAW3I%2FC9AhTY%2FaDgzkAO6tKN2FhpyhCcE0%3D&h=b8ffa509\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n<br />\n現有文宣集合 (Google Drive)<br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/open?id=128hRA8sm5aa2jUlNJAzPtGkYt2_3n-z2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fopen%3Fid%3D128hRA8sm5aa2jUlNJAzPtGkYt2_3n-z2&d=TNp%2FFCzVUvAW3I%2FC9AhTY%2FaDgzkAO6tKN2FhpyhCcE0%3D&h=13ae533d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/open?id=128hRA8sm5aa2jUlNJAzPtGkYt2_3n-z2</a><br />\n請隨便使用，用自己的方法幫忙發送文宣出去，感謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba83d707253952f57ce2f19262d698a0e6999327","tid":1507840,"uid":25635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T10:20:28.000Z","msg":"唔洗開冷氣都起哂雞皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a35973109cc491ec7fc88213f0a1360e47570372","tid":1507840,"uid":258208,"like":0,"dis